			"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Damage to one of the forges caused hot coals to spill onto the floor and set fire to discarded materials. The fire is now out of control and is spreading across the room. At the start of the encounter, the fire fills a 6-square-by-6-square area.</i></p><p><b>Hazard:</b> A 6-by-6 square area has a fire.</p>",
