			"type":"feature",
			"img":"icons/svg/cancel.svg",
			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<ul><li><b>Acrobatics DC 20:</b> A character can move into a square of raging fire or a square adjacent to the raging fire without triggering the attack with a successful check.</li><li>Two gallons of water destroys 1 square of raging fire.</li><li>Targeting 1 or more squares with a water attack automatically destroys the fire in those squares.</li></ul>",
