				"description":{
					"value":"<p><b>Free Action</b></p><p><b>Melee</b> 1</p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Target: </b> The triggering creature</p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Attack: </b>+6 vs. Reflex</p><p>Special The raging fire gains a +5 bonus to its attack roll if the target stands inside the fire.</p><p><b>Hit: </b> 2d6 fire damage and ongoing 5 fire damage (save ends).</p><p><b>Miss: </b> Half damage, and no ongoing damage.</p><p>Effect The fire also provides concealment to all creatures inside it and within 2 squares of it.</p><p>Special Each time the fire attacks, it spreads into its target's space whether it hits or misses.</p>",
